briefdescription.para: This control is a native wrapper around the Safari web browsing engine.

detaileddescription.para: This wrapper differs from the one in wxWebView in that this version supports functionality specific to WebKit, such as having RunScript return a value, which is a very critical feature in many web embedding scenarios.
This class is only available on OSX.
